-- British Soldier Is Killed by Explosion in Afghanistan's Helmand Province
-- Mike Harrison
-- 2010-07-18T06:06:12Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-18/british-soldier-is-killed-by-explosion-in-afghanistan-s-helmand-province.html

          
          
             A soldier from the Royal Logistic
Corps was killed in an explosion during an operation in the
Nahr-e Saraj District of Helmand Province, in Afghanistan,
yesterday, the Ministry of Defence in London said in an e-mailed
statement.  
          
          


  


        